<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dʿwtny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- dʿwtny ạ̹ny ạ̉ʿysẖ dạymaⁿạ mʿạk
 wạ̉skn dạymaⁿạ fy ḥmạk
 wạ̉frḥ wyạk wạ̉nạ ạ̹mty̱ yạ rby hạqbl dʿwtk
 wạ̹mty̱ hạkwn yạ rby sbb lfrḥtk
 ạlqrạr- dʿwtny ạ̉ḥbbtny nạdytny dʿwtny
 2- ạ̉ḥbbtny wkmạn mt ʿsẖạny ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb kẖdt
 mkạny wạ̉nạ ạljạny
 wạ̉nạ ạ̹mty̱ yạ rby hạslm ʿmry lyk
 w ạ̹mty̱ hạtwb yạ rby sạʿdny ạ̉rjʿ ạ̹lyk
 3- nạdytny tʿạlwạ yạ mtʿbyn wyạkl wạḥd ḥzyn
 ạ̉nạ rạʿy ạ̉myn
 wạ̉nạ ạ̹mty̱ yạ rby hạrmy ḥmly ʿlyk
 wạ̹mty̱ tkwn ḥyạty kẖzfẗ mạ byn ạ̹ydyk</lyrics>
<author>jwrj nạdy, jwrj nạdy</author>
<hymn_number>9647</hymn_number>
</song>